      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is done, divide the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>& pepper </strong>evenly between the pizza base[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the mozzarella has melted and the pizza base[s] is crisp – this is your <strong>smoky BBQ free range chicken pizza</strong></p>",
